description: Least positive sequence with Hankel transform {1,1,1,1,1,...}.
comments: Hankel transform {t(n)} of {a(n)} is given by t(n) = Det[{a(1), a(2), ..., a(n)}, {a(2), a(3), ..., a(n+1)}, ..., {a(n), a(n+1), ..., a(2n-1)}].
links: M. Garcia Armas, B. A. Sethuraman, A note on the Hankel Transform of the Central Binomial Coefficients, JIS 11 (2008) 08.5.8
J. W. Layman, The Hankel Transform and Some of its Properties, J. Integer Sequences, 4 (2001), #01.1.5.
author: _John W. Layman_, Jul 15 2000
extensions: Next term is too large to include.
